nodes.text: Pisk was a male individual from Naboo who lived during the time of the Galactic Civil War. By the time of the Battle of Yavin, Pisk and his friend Tinrilo x'Rilsam, a retired Royal Naboo Security Forces agent, decided to dedicate to history and exploration of the galaxy. While x'Rilsam wandered to many worlds, Pisk preferred to focus first on one planet: Dathomir. Both planed to meet up at the cantina in Bestine after their explorations had been drawn to a close.
